threads.title: 820-3435 board fan spin all rail there , no external disply or turn on
threads.message:
got this mac air with 820-3435 board , fan spin , all power rail is there, cpu voltage is there, it might have slight liquid damage, copper round pad are slight discolour,  all rail have power, PPVRTC_G3H there, 

only missing power rail is l3095,  and L7701,     cpu turn hot, , All_pwr is good,   any idea what is wrong ?

threads.title: 820-3435 board fan spin all rail there , no external disply or turn on
threads.message:
Try new BIOS first.
PLT_RESET_L and BUF_PLT_RST_L both present?
Do you get USB activity?
